<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.7.3">
<l>añcuvaṉ veñcoṉṉaṅkā yarakkarkulap pāvaitaṉṉai</l>
<l>veñciṉa mūkkarinta viṟalōntiṟaṅ kēṭkiṉmeyyē</l>
<l>pañciya mellaṭiyem paṇaittōḷipa rakkaḻintu</l>
<l>vañciyan taṇpaṇaicūḻ vayalālipu kuvarkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I fear, ladies, if I hear of the ability of the strong man,</l>
<l>Who [with] a burning rage, severed the nose of the girl in the ogre clan,</l>
<l rend="indent">that the cruel words are true.</l>
<l>[With] the body of my bamboo-armed [girl] failing, [her] feet as soft as cotton,</l>
<l>Are they setting out for Āli where the paddy fields are encircled</l>
<l rend="indent">by fine, cool bamboo [and] vañci creepers?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
